<plot>Evelyn, bound by her own curiosity sits waiting, hoping that this time will be different...that her blind date won't be so blind, that love really can find everyone. When a computer arrives to her table the jaunt into the surreal begins. Communication Breakdown is a romantic comedy that takes a look at what may lie ahead for all of us in the funny world of dating in the 21st century. How our own sense of curiosity and need for connection has led us down a path we may not soon return from, and how love really can be sparked in the most unusual of places. Hal has finally arrived.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?112571</url></doc>
